    "The evaluation of the post-hoc survey shows that the experimental group perceives a speed gain in military analysis through AI functions.",
    "However, it should be noted that the participants are not experts in the field of military analysis.",
    "Yet, their evaluation is in line with the findings by Perboli et al. (2021).",
    "In the context of the labeling of aviation accident documents, the use of AI functions for the partial automation of expert work has reduced the overall investigation time by 30%.",
